data.title: Surnames
data.text:
SMITH, MOORE, MYERS, CANTRELL out of Rhea, Meigs Co. TN as well

as Ham. Co., James Co. TN and LONG,

CANSLER, THOMPSON out of Union/Fannin

Co. GA, Ham., James, Meigs, Rhea Co. TN

MULLINS in all of East TN

I am stuck on wife of Lesley MYERS b abt 1807

Greene Co. TN who md. Indianna

(?) and had first son ie Wm. R. MYERS in

Hawkins Co. TN before moving to

Miegs/Rhea. Indianna's maiden name is

unknown and I've looked at RILEY,

REYNOLDS, BELL as well as other possiblities. I'm really stuck on this.

She died and Lesley remd. Mary GREGORY

from James Co. TN. Mary

and some of the MYERS kids ended up in

Ham. Co. TN.

Debbie Woolf
